<h1 id="toc0"><span>Usage</span></h1>
<p>To import this theme to your page, put the following anywhere inside it:</p>
<div class="code">
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include&#32;:scp-wiki:theme:creepypasta]]</span></p>
</div>
<p>The standard CSS @import method won't work. This is intentional (thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3075960&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607163368" alt="stormbreath" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3075960)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/stormbreath" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3075960); return false;">stormbreath</a></span> for providing the CSS code!). Importing the theme using <span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">[[include]]</span> adds your page to a list of Backlinks. This is useful for seeing what pages would be affected when this theme is updated, and allows any errors caused by that to be noticed and corrected much faster.</p>
<p>You can view any page's Backlinks by clicking &quot;+ Options&quot; at the bottom of the page, then &quot;Backlinks&quot;.</p>
<hr />
